OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FA man remains in custody following his
OL,7,Farrest on suspicion of attempted
OL,8,Fmurder after seven people were injured
OL,9,Fwhen a car hit pedestrians in Derby.
OL,11,FCounter terrorism officers are
OL,12,Fassisting with the investigation into
OL,13,Fthe incident, which happened in Friar
OL,14,FGate at about 9.30pm on Saturday, but
OL,15,Fpolice are keeping an open mind about
OL,16,Fpotential motives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
