OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774850710
OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FThe 36-year-old Derby man, who is
OL,7,Foriginally from India but has lived in
OL,8,Fthe UK for a number of years, was
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,10,Fmurder, causing serious injury through
OL,11,Fdangerous driving, inflicting grievous
OL,12,Fbodily harm with intent, and dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving, Derbyshire Police said.
OL,15,FSeven people were treated at the scene
OL,16,Fand taken to hospital with a range of
OL,17,Fserious but not life-threatening
OL,18,Finjuries, after they were hit by a
OL,19,Fblack Suzuki Swift, the force added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774850710
OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FThe force said the support of counter
OL,7,Fterrorism officers does not mean the
OL,8,Fincident is currently being treated as
OL,9,Fterrorism.
OL,11,FDerbyshire Police said in a statement:
OL,12,F"Derbyshire detectives are leading the
OL,13,Finvestigation with the support of
OL,14,FCounter Terrorism Policing colleagues,
OL,15,Fwhich is common practice for an
OL,16,Fincident of this nature, and are
OL,17,Fkeeping an open mind about the
OL,18,Fpotential motives.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774850710
OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"Although counter terrorism officers
OL,7,Fare assisting us with those early
OL,8,Finvestigations, this does not mean the
OL,9,Fincident is currently being treated as
OL,10,Fterrorism."
OL,12,FChief Superintendent Emma Aldred, who
OL,13,Fleads policing in Derby, told a media
OL,14,Fbriefing on Sunday that the suspected
OL,15,Fdriver was arrested on the other side
OL,16,Fof the city centre seven minutes after
OL,17,Fthe incident.
OL,19,FShe said: "He was safely stopped in
OL,20,FStation Approach, where the bridge
OL,21,Fcrosses over towards Pride Park.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]{D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774850710
OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"This swift action would not have been
OL,7,Fpossible without eyewitnesses who
OL,8,Fcontacted us about the vehicle's
OL,9,Fwhereabouts as it was driven away from
OL,10,Fthe scene and around the city centre."
OL,12,FShe added that the force believes it
OL,13,Fis an isolated incident, and there is
OL,14,Fno wider risk to the public.
OL,16,FThe Home Secretary is being kept
OL,17,Fupdated on the incident, Education
OL,18,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson told the
OL,19,FBBC's Sunday With Laura Kuenssberg
OL,20,Fprogramme.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]
