OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FDetectives are urging anyone who has
OL,7,Ffootage of the incident taking place,
OL,8,For dashcam footage capturing the car
OL,9,Fbefore or after, to come forward.
OL,11,FThe force said it is thought the
OL,12,Fsuspect drove off along Friar Gate
OL,13,Faway from the city centre, towards
OL,14,FAshbourne Road, then into Bridge
OL,15,FStreet, Lodge Lane towards Five Lamps,
OL,16,FGarden Street and Duffield Road before
OL,17,Fgoing into St Alkmund's Way.
OL,19,FThe visibly damaged vehicle was then
OL,20,Fstopped by police a short time later
OL,21,Fat Station Approach, the force said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
