OL,3,CMan, 36, remains in custody after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FAnyone with information that could
OL,7,Fhelp officers with their investigation
OL,8,Fshould contact the force online or by
OL,9,Fcalling 101, quoting incident 1131 of
OL,10,FMarch 28.
OL,12,FInformation can also be given
OL,13,Fanonymously to the independent charity
OL,14,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111, or by
OL,15,Fvisiting its website crimestoppers-
OL,16,Fuk.org/.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
